<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport"
        content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>너, 운동된 거야</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tensorflow/tfjs@1.3.1/dist/tf.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@teachablemachine/pose@0.8/dist/teachablemachine-pose.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/teachable.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/maze-builder.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/mazing.js"></script>
    <script src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.6.0/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&family=Song+Myung&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/game.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/tutorial.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="main" id="main">
        <img src="../img/logo.png" id="logo" />

        <!-- <h1 id="title">너, 운동된 거야</h1>
        <h3>동작을 취해 캐릭터를 움직여 미로를 탈출해보세요!</h3> -->
<div class="main-content">
    
            <!-- Webcam -->
            <div id="webcam">
                <h2 id="name">
                    <%= nickname %> 님!
                </h2>
                <div>
                    <canvas class="card-img-top" id="canvas" ></canvas>
                </div>
                <h1 id="time">00:00</h1>
                <div id="label-container"></div>
                <p>자세 인식 중...</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p>가만히 서 있기</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p>⬇️ 스쿼트 하기 ⬇️</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p>⬆️ 팔 벌려 뛰기 ⬆️</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p>⬅️ 왼쪽으로 스트레칭 ⬅️</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
                <p>➡️ 오른쪽으로 스트레칭 ➡️</p>
                <div class="progress-bar__container">
                    <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Tutorial -->
            <div class="container-carousel">
                <input type="radio" name="slider" id="item-1" checked>
                <input type="radio" name="slider" id="item-2">
                <input type="radio" name="slider" id="item-3">
                <input type="radio" name="slider" id="item-4">
                <input type="radio" name="slider" id="item-5">
    
                <div class="cards">
                    <label class="card-carousel" for="item-1" id="song-1">
                        <img src="../img/stand.gif" class="cardImg">
                    </label>
                    <label class="card-carousel" for="item-2" id="song-2">
                        <img src="../img/squat.gif" class="cardImg">
                    </label>
                    <label class="card-carousel" for="item-3" id="song-3">
                        <img src="../img/what.gif" class="cardImg">
                    </label>
                    <label class="card-carousel" for="item-4" id="song-4">
                        <img src="../img/left.gif" class="cardImg">
                    </label>
                    <label class="card-carousel" for="item-5" id="song-5">
                        <img src="../img/right.gif" class="cardImg">
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="player">
                    <div class="upper-part">
                        <div class="info-area" id="test">
                            <label class="song-info" id="song-info-1">
                                <div class="title">가만히 서 있으세요. 캐릭터가 가만히 있게 됩니다.</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="song-info" id="song-info-2">
                                <div class="title">스쿼트를 하세요. 캐릭터가 아래로 이동합니다.</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="song-info" id="song-info-3">
                                <div class="title">팔 벌려 뛰기를 하세요. 캐릭터가 위로 이동합니다.</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="song-info" id="song-info-4">
                                <div class="title">왼쪽으로 스트레칭 하세요. 캐릭터가 왼쪽으로 이동합니다.</div>
                            </label>
                            <label class="song-info" id="song-info-5">
                                <div class="title">오른쪽으로 스트레칭 하세요. 캐릭터가 오른쪽으로 이동합니다.</div>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div> <img src="../img/arrow.png" id="arrow" onclick="startGame();"> </div>
            </div>
</div>
    </div>
    <script>
        function startGame() {
            const name = "<%= nickname %>";
            const level = Number(<%= level %>);
            location.href = `/play/${level}?nickname=${name}`;
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>